      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p class=\"alert alert-info\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-color-blue120\">This content is available to customers with active <a href=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/en-us/articles/360014400932\" target=\"_self\">Liferay Enterprise Search (LES)</a> subscriptions</span></p>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"703\">To activate your Enterprise Search product, Administrators should navigate to the <a href=\"support.liferay.com\" target=\"_self\">Customer Portal</a>'s Product Activation tab on the left sidebar navigation and select Enterprise Search. For more details please refer <a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/how-do-i-activate-my-enterprise-search-product-video-tutorial\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"undefined\">this video tutorial</a>.</p>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"703\">The license provided through Customer Portal can be installed on the Elasticsearch clusters covered by your project's subscriptions. The license is time based and typically expires at the end of your Enterprise Search subscription term.</p>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"1045\">To get started with Liferay Enterprise Search:</p>\n<h2>1. Download and Install Elasticsearch</h2>\n<ul>\n<li data-renderer-start-pos=\"1134\">Elasticsearch Downloads: <span><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" data-testid=\"hover-card-trigger-wrapper\"><a class=\"css-6uefhw eeajecn0\" tabindex=\"0\" href=\"https://www.elastic.co/downloads/elasticsearch\" data-testid=\"inline-card-resolved-view\"><span class=\"css-1p7ax5 e158gagu2\" data-testid=\"inline-card-icon-and-title\"><span class=\"smart-link-title-wrapper css-0 e158gagu8\">Download Elasticsearch</span></span></a></span></span>\n</li>\n<li data-renderer-start-pos=\"1165\">Docker Images: <a class=\"css-tgpl01\" title=\"https://www.docker.elastic.co/\" href=\"https://www.docker.elastic.co/\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">https://www.docker.elastic.co</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Select a version <a class=\"css-tgpl01\" title=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/search-engine-compatibility-matrix\" href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/search-engine-compatibility-matrix\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">compatible with Liferay</a>.</p>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"1256\">Installation Instructions:</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-renderer-start-pos=\"1286\">\n<span><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" data-testid=\"hover-card-trigger-wrapper\"><a class=\"css-6uefhw eeajecn0\" tabindex=\"0\" href=\"https://learn.liferay.com/dxp/7.x/en/using-search/installing-and-upgrading-a-search-engine/elasticsearch.html\" data-testid=\"inline-card-resolved-view\"><span class=\"css-1p7ax5 e158gagu2\" data-testid=\"inline-card-icon-and-title\"><span class=\"smart-link-title-wrapper css-0 e158gagu8\">Elasticsearch</span></span></a></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li data-renderer-start-pos=\"1292\">For Liferay DXP please find the related documentation in <a class=\"css-tgpl01\" title=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/en-us\" href=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/en-us\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">Liferay Help Center</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-renderer-start-pos=\"1375\">To install the attached license in your Elasticsearch cluster, please follow the Elasticsearch documentation, for example for Elasticsearch 7.x: <a class=\"css-tgpl01\" title=\"https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/update-license.html\" href=\"https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/update-license.html\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">Update License</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>2. Download and Install Liferay Enterprise Search Apps</h2>\n<p>Starting from Liferay DXP 7.4, Enterprise Search Apps are included in Liferay DXP and do not need to be downloaded separately.</p>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"1722\">For Liferay DXP 7.3 and below, Enterprise Search Apps can be downloaded from Liferay Help Center: <a class=\"css-tgpl01\" title=\"https://customer.liferay.com/en/downloads?p_p_id=com_liferay_osb_customer_downloads_display_web_DownloadsDisplayPortlet&amp;_com_liferay_osb_customer_downloads_display_web_DownloadsDisplayPortlet_productAssetCategoryId=118191013&amp;_com_liferay_osb_customer_downloads_display_web_DownloadsDisplayPortlet_fileTypeAssetCategoryId=118191060\" href=\"https://customer.liferay.com/en/downloads?p_p_id=com_liferay_osb_customer_downloads_display_web_DownloadsDisplayPortlet&amp;_com_liferay_osb_customer_downloads_display_web_DownloadsDisplayPortlet_productAssetCategoryId=118191013&amp;_com_liferay_osb_customer_downloads_display_web_DownloadsDisplayPortlet_fileTypeAssetCategoryId=118191060\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">Download here</a> (under the Enterprise Search category)</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-renderer-start-pos=\"1876\">Liferay Enterprise Search Cross-Cluster Replication</li>\n<li data-renderer-start-pos=\"1931\">Liferay Enterprise Search Learning to Rank</li>\n<li data-renderer-start-pos=\"1977\">Liferay Enterprise Search Monitoring\n<ul>\n<li data-renderer-start-pos=\"2017\">To use monitoring, you must also download Kibana: <a class=\"css-tgpl01\" title=\"https://www.elastic.co/downloads/kibana\" href=\"https://www.elastic.co/downloads/kibana\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">https://www.elastic.co/downloads/kibana</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-renderer-start-pos=\"2112\">Liferay Enterprise Search Security</li>\n<li data-renderer-start-pos=\"2150\">Liferay Enterprise Search Experiences: Blueprints</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"2205\">Installation Instructions: <a class=\"css-tgpl01\" title=\"https://learn.liferay.com/dxp/latest/en/using-search/liferay-enterprise-search.html\" href=\"https://learn.liferay.com/dxp/latest/en/using-search/liferay-enterprise-search.html\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">https://learn.liferay.com/dxp/latest/en/using-search/liferay-enterprise-search.html</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li data-renderer-start-pos=\"2320\">For Liferay DXP please find the related documentation in <a class=\"css-tgpl01\" title=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/en-us\" href=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/en-us\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">Liferay Help Center</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"2401\">See the complete list of LES components <a class=\"css-tgpl01\" title=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/en-us/articles/360014400932\" href=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/en-us/articles/360014400932\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">here</a>.</p>\n<h2>3. Support and Troubleshooting</h2>\n<p>Get familiar with support for Liferay Enterprise Search:</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-renderer-start-pos=\"2540\"><a class=\"css-tgpl01\" title=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/search-engine-compatibility-matrix#Liferay-Enterprise-Search\" href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/search-engine-compatibility-matrix#Liferay-Enterprise-Search\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">Liferay Enterprise Search Compatibility Matrix</a></li>\n<li data-renderer-start-pos=\"2590\"><a class=\"css-tgpl01\" title=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/les-how-to-install-and-run-the-elastic-support-diagnostics-troubleshooting-utility\" href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/les-how-to-install-and-run-the-elastic-support-diagnostics-troubleshooting-utility\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">How to use the Elastic Support Diagnostic Tool</a></li>\n<li data-renderer-start-pos=\"2640\"><a class=\"css-tgpl01\" title=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/en-us/articles/360016476612-Liferay-Enterprise-Search-End-of-Life-Policy\" href=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/en-us/articles/360016476612-Liferay-Enterprise-Search-End-of-Life-Policy\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">End of Life Policy</a></li>\n<li data-renderer-start-pos=\"2662\"><a class=\"css-tgpl01\" title=\"https://support.liferay.com/other-liferay-products#Enterprise-Search\" href=\"https://support.liferay.com/other-liferay-products#Enterprise-Search\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">Support Coverage</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"2682\">If you have any questions or issues with your Liferay Enterprise Search subscription, please contact Liferay Support through the <a href=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/requests/new\" target=\"_self\">Help Center</a>.</p>"
      },
